# Database Architecture

## AI Business Operations Platform (ABOP)

## Overview

The AI Business Operations Platform uses Airtable as the central operational database and single source of truth.

The database architecture was designed using a relational model to connect customer information, sales activities, operational workflows, AI processing, and business intelligence reporting.

---

