# Core Tables

## 1. Leads Table

### Purpose

Stores all incoming prospects and business opportunities.

### Fields

| Field             | Type          | Description                              |
| ----------------- | ------------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| Lead Name         | Text          | Contact person                           |
| Company           | Text          | Business/company name                    |
| Email             | Email         | Lead contact                             |
| Phone             | Phone         | Contact number                           |
| Lead Source       | Single Select | Website, Referral, LinkedIn, Facebook    |
| Service Requested | Multi Select  | Requested service                        |
| Status            | Single Select | New, Contacted, Qualified, Proposal Sent |
| Qualification     | Single Select | Hot, Warm, Cold                          |
| Urgency           | Single Select | Low, Medium, High, Emergency             |
| AI Summary        | Long Text     | AI-generated lead analysis               |

---

# 2. Opportunities Table

## Purpose

Tracks sales pipeline and revenue forecasting.

### Fields

| Field               | Type          | Description                   |
| ------------------- | ------------- | ----------------------------- |
| Opportunity Name    | Text          | Deal name                     |
| Deal Value          | Currency      | Estimated revenue             |
| Sales Stage         | Single Select | Pipeline stage                |
| Probability         | Percentage    | Closing likelihood            |
| Expected Close Date | Date          | Forecast close date           |
| AI Win Analysis     | Long Text     | AI-generated sales prediction |

---

# 3. Clients Table

## Purpose

Manages converted customers and customer success activities.

### Fields

| Field                 | Type          | Description                    |
| --------------------- | ------------- | ------------------------------ |
| Client Name           | Text          | Customer/company               |
| Primary Contact       | Text          | Main contact                   |
| Email                 | Email         | Client email                   |
| Status                | Single Select | Active, Onboarding             |
| Start Date            | Date          | Customer start date            |
| Client Health Summary | Long Text     | AI-generated customer insights |

---

# 4. Tasks Table

## Purpose

Manages business workflows and operational activities.

### Fields

| Field             | Type          | Description                         |
| ----------------- | ------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| Task Name         | Text          | Activity name                       |
| Description       | Long Text     | Task details                        |
| Assigned Team     | Single Select | Responsible department              |
| Priority          | Single Select | Low, Medium, High                   |
| Due Date          | Date          | Deadline                            |
| Status            | Single Select | Not Started, In Progress, Completed |
| AI Recommendation | Long Text     | AI workflow suggestion              |

---

# 5. KPI Table

## Purpose

Tracks business performance and executive metrics.

### Fields

| Field            | Type          | Description              |
| ---------------- | ------------- | ------------------------ |
| KPI Name         | Text          | Metric name              |
| Current Value    | Number        | Current performance      |
| Target Value     | Number        | Business goal            |
| Reporting Period | Single Select | Weekly, Monthly          |
| Date Updated     | Date          | Last update              |
| AI Insight       | Long Text     | Generated recommendation |

