# Data Relationships

## Leads → Opportunities

A qualified lead can become a sales opportunity.

Example:

```
New Lead
   ↓
Qualified Lead
   ↓
Opportunity Created
```

---

## Opportunities → Clients

A successful opportunity becomes a client.

Example:

```
Closed Won Deal
       ↓
Client Account Created
```

---

## Clients → Tasks

Clients generate operational tasks.

Example:

```
New Client
    ↓
Onboarding Tasks
    ↓
Service Delivery
```

---

